  "title": "Deliciously Spicy Indian Basmati Rice Biryani",
  "description": "A spicy and light ovo-vegetarian friendly Indian dish featuring basmati rice, this biryani is perfect for meal prep, with an al-dente finish and a blend of aromatic spices.",
