  "instructions": [
    "Heat ghee in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and let them sizzle for a few seconds.",
    "Add chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add grated ginger and minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add coriander powder, turmeric powder, and red chili powder and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add basmati rice and cook for 2-3 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add water and salt, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 15-20 minutes or until the rice is cooked and the water is absorbed.",
    "Fluff the rice with a fork and stir in chopped hard boiled eggs.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
  ],
